23/carima-streamlining-african-car-market5593?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Carima: Streamlining African Car Market</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Caloha’s 3-day Display of Chery at  Ikeja City Mall Captivates Customers" href="../../../2024/03/23/calohas-3-day-display-of-chery-at-ikeja-city-mall-captivates-customers5593.html?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Page-1-Pic-1-Carloha.jpeg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Caloha’s 3-day Display of Chery at  Ikeja City Mall Captivates Customers" href="../../../2024/03/23/calohas-3-day-display-of-chery-at-ikeja-city-mall-captivates-customers5593.html?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Caloha’s 3-day Display of Chery at  Ikeja City Mall Captivates Customers</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Toyota Nigeria Presents 9 School Children for Another Global Dream Car Art Contest" href="../../../2024/03/23/toyota-nigeria-presents-9-school-children-for-another-global-dream-car-art-contest5593?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Screenshot_20240323-112049.jpg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Toyota Nigeria Presents 9 School Children for Anoth